    "2a680ed28e2e7e99": {
      "translation": "इन अनुकूलित नोड्स को स्थापित करें:",
      "model": "translategemma:12b",
      "timestamp": 1772021434605
    },
    "e661069f4a09edb3": {
      "translation": "**मुख्य भाग:**\n- [ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite](https://github.com/Kosinkadink/ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite) - वीडियो एन्कोडिंग",
      "model": "translategemma:12b",
      "timestamp": 1772021434605
    },
    "8c9c9c554590438b": {
      "translation": "**मॉडल-विशिष्ट:**\n- LTX-Video 2: ComfyUI का अंतर्निहित समर्थन (नवीनतम संस्करण)\n- Hunyuan 1.5: [ComfyUI-HunyuanVideo](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-HunyuanVideoWrapper)\n- Wan: [ComfyUI-WanVideoWrapper](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-WanVideoWrapper)\n- AnimateDiff: [ComfyUI-AnimateDiff-Evolved](https://github.com/Kosinkadink/ComfyUI-AnimateDiff-Evolved)",
      "model": "translategemma:12b",
      "timestamp": 1772021434605
